divs: sighting detailsas we were driving up our street, my daughters and i saw a grayish\dark gray colored jellyfish like looking object. it was waving in the air like a stingray would in the water. it just floated in the air and then totally vanished. it was about the size of two cruise ships stacked on top of each other. it was big, much bigger than a 747. if we had to guess, we would say it was about two miles from where we were driving. i would really be curious to know if anyone else saw this so i would know that i am not crazy.

Summary: Just before noon, as we were driving, we saw a jelly fish/ray type object hovering over our neighborhood.
